description: White fish fillets baked in a parcel of squash, spinach and olives, finished with basil sauce.
name: Steamed Fish, Olive & Herb Parcels Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Place parcels on a baking tray and bake for 10-12 minutes or until fish is cooked. Scatter with spinach leaves, to serve.
